-themed Galaxy Buds are too cute]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> 《精灵宝可梦》可能是日本的系列产品，但与世界各地的人们一样，韩国企业集团三星继续通过其<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAacOUGZitpWlpMfmSIWDeCQjMTzga6ciFXGkc1vbBrBo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.samsung.com%2Fkr%2F%25EC%2582%25BC%25EC%2584%25B1%25EC%25A0%2584%25EC%259E%2590-%25EA%25B0%25A4%25EB%259F%25AD%25EC%258B%259C-%25EB%25B2%2584%25EC%25A6%25882%25C2%25B7%25EB%25B2%2584%25EC%25A6%25882-%25ED%2594%2584%25EB%25A1%259C-%25ED%258F%25AC%25EC%25BC%2593%25EB%25AA%25AC-%25EC%25BC%2580%25EC%259D%25B4%25EC%258A%25A4-%25ED%258C%25A8" class="rapid-with-clickid">最新的《精灵宝可梦》主题产品</a>展现出与该系列的亲缘关系。这家电子公司宣布推出新的 Pokémon Packs，其中包括三款新的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-buds-2-review-150002889.html">Galaxy Buds 2</a>保护壳，设计外观分别为 Jigglypuff、Ditto 和 Snorlax。除了可爱的保护套外，套装还配有相应的贴纸，并可选择售价 129,000 韩元（99 美元）的 Galaxy Buds 2 或售价 199,000 韩元（152 美元）的 Galaxy Buds 2 Pro。</p><p>三星以经典选项开始了这一系列，于 2022 年 5 月推出了<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL25ld3Muc2Ftc3VuZy5jb20vc2cvcG9rZW1vbi10aGVtZWQtYWNjZXNzb3JpZXMtZm9yLWdhbGF4eS16LWZsaXA0LTVnLWJ1ZHMyLXByby1hbmQtd2F0Y2g1IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJlNWI3OTg5OC1iNTc5LTQ1NTktOTdmMC03NmY1MWYzNTgzNDgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXD-rocRaxUaVAArEeE8WwqZS6TKU-eCf7LDoZUJBUwI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.samsung.com%2Fsg%2Fpokemon-themed-accessories-for-galaxy-z-flip4-5g-buds2-pro-and-watch5" class="rapid-with-clickid">适用于 Galaxy Buds 2 Pro 和标准版耳机的精灵球保护壳</a>。这款限量版商品在一小时内就售罄，因此该公司想要发布这一产品并不奇怪。更多神奇宝贝主题选项。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-z-flip-3-pokemon-edition-095257752.html">三星 Galaxy Z